ibs ignition-math2 should output -lm as well.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>The generated pkgconfig file ignition-math2.pc should specify -lm under the Libs: section since there are template classes like Quaternion (and probably others) that use cmath functions. When I use those generic classes, my code has to be linked directly against libm, so pkg-config --libs ignition-math2 should output -lm as well.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2015-12-11T20:35:17.093783+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2017-12-19T01:15:35.459164+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 36}